WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.376 --> 01:37.808
=Episode 28=

01:44.400 --> 01:45.760
What Princess Ding said

01:45.920 --> 01:48.599
reminded me of something
that chills me to the bone.

01:48.879 --> 01:51.799
Not long ago, Marquis Muyang's
confidant Zhang Hengyuan

01:52.280 --> 01:54.200
attempted to assassinate Zhong Xingtong.

01:54.840 --> 01:56.760
Last night, another
of his confidants, Zhao Ting,

01:57.319 --> 01:58.959
tried to assassinate Princess Ding.

01:59.200 --> 02:02.079
Two shocking assassination attempts
were in such quick succession,

02:02.319 --> 02:04.879
and the masterminds behind them
were both confidants

02:05.280 --> 02:08.479
with deep ties to Marquis Muyang.

02:08.479 --> 02:11.039
Isn't that far too much
of a coincidence?

02:11.639 --> 02:14.879
I wonder what excellent explanation
Marquis Muyang has for that.

02:17.960 --> 02:19.759
Your Majesties,

02:20.039 --> 02:22.319
it's purely a crude
and baseless frame-up,

02:22.759 --> 02:24.639
attempting to implicate
a key court official.

02:25.080 --> 02:26.080
If this trend takes hold,

02:26.400 --> 02:29.879
I fear that everyone in this court
will live in fear from now on,

02:30.280 --> 02:32.719
all vulnerable to being implicated
by fabricated charges.

02:33.120 --> 02:35.719
I have no defense to offer,

02:36.280 --> 02:37.840
nor do I need one.

02:38.800 --> 02:41.639
I beg Your Majesties
to see clearly into this matter.

02:43.879 --> 02:47.360
Zhao Ting is dead,
but Chen Longxiang is still alive.

02:47.840 --> 02:49.560
There is no evidence against Zhao Ting,

02:50.439 --> 02:54.319
but the evidence for what Chen Longxiang
has confessed is irrefutable.

02:59.639 --> 03:01.360
Your Majesties,

03:01.879 --> 03:04.439
I interrogated the key suspect
Chen Longxiang overnight,

03:05.280 --> 03:08.000
and he has confessed to his crimes
without reservation.

03:17.639 --> 03:19.000
From his private residence,

03:19.159 --> 03:22.439
I uncovered several secret letters
between Marquis Muyang and Cangbei,

03:22.680 --> 03:23.759
all detailing

03:23.879 --> 03:27.199
how to smuggle Dachu's
weaponry to Cangbei.

03:27.639 --> 03:30.639
Also, there are records of Cangbei's
bribes to Marquis Muyang,

03:30.639 --> 03:32.879
including land deeds,
properties, horses,

03:33.039 --> 03:36.080
and a ledger tracing the flow
of all illicit funds.

03:37.000 --> 03:38.256
The evidence is irrefutable.

03:47.639 --> 03:49.159
Your Majesties,

03:49.919 --> 03:51.800
no matter what evidence is in that box,

03:52.080 --> 03:55.080
I beg you to grant me
a chance to prove my innocence.

03:57.520 --> 03:59.560
Since both sides
present conflicting accounts,

03:59.680 --> 04:02.159
and the evidence has been
presented before the throne,

04:02.280 --> 04:05.039
the truth can be revealed
upon examination.

04:05.639 --> 04:07.439
The Duke speaks wisely.

04:08.000 --> 04:10.159
Marquis Muyang, please remain calm.

04:10.599 --> 04:13.552
Their Majesties are wise and discerning
and will deliver a fair judgment.

04:13.680 --> 04:16.040
If Marquis Muyang is truly innocent,

04:16.160 --> 04:19.120
I petition to preside over this case

04:19.839 --> 04:21.639
to restore justice for Marquis Muyang.

04:26.560 --> 04:28.160
Your Majesties,

04:29.199 --> 04:32.360
I have one more matter to report,
as it is of national importance.

04:33.000 --> 04:35.639
And Marquis Muyang
is also a key figure in this.

04:41.680 --> 04:42.639
Eight years ago,

04:44.839 --> 04:46.864
in the Heiyun Cavalry's
alleged rebellion case,

04:47.279 --> 04:49.639
the presiding judge was Marquis Muyang.

04:50.040 --> 04:51.439
His investigation concluded

04:51.879 --> 04:55.040
that the Heiyun Cavalry mobilized
without an edict and plotted treason.

04:55.800 --> 04:59.439
But all the so-called dispatches,
secret letters, and evidence

04:59.879 --> 05:02.319
were fabricated by Marquis Muyang.

05:02.439 --> 05:04.639
He tortured for confessions
and framed loyal officials.

05:04.759 --> 05:05.959
Utter nonsense!

05:09.600 --> 05:12.920
Your Majesty, for all the cases
I handled back then,

05:12.920 --> 05:16.240
each and every one of them
was supported by irrefutable evidence.

05:17.480 --> 05:19.439
This case is of grave importance.

05:20.279 --> 05:21.560
It's sealed for eight years.

05:21.879 --> 05:24.600
Princess Ding, you're accusing
a key court official.

05:24.879 --> 05:26.160
Do you have solid proof?

05:35.439 --> 05:36.279
I do.

05:53.079 --> 05:54.639
This is the late Emperor's edict.

05:59.279 --> 06:00.560
The edict clearly commands

06:00.920 --> 06:03.279
the late Prince Ding, Mo Xiuwen,
to lead the Heiyun Cavalry

06:03.279 --> 06:05.008
to the capital to protect the throne.

06:05.959 --> 06:08.319
It has the late Emperor's
authentic handwriting and seal.

06:08.800 --> 06:11.279
A simple comparison
will reveal its authenticity.

06:18.639 --> 06:19.439
Wait.

06:29.040 --> 06:32.160
Since it's the root of disaster,
it must be destroyed.

06:41.800 --> 06:43.399
Your Majesties,

06:43.639 --> 06:45.639
I can stake my life on the guarantee

06:45.720 --> 06:48.120
that this is indeed
the late Emperor's edict.

07:04.279 --> 07:05.079
Prince Ding.

07:44.959 --> 07:47.879
Zhou Jing, what else do you have to say?

07:51.632 --> 07:53.456
(Edict)

07:57.879 --> 08:00.920
I, Mo Xiuyao, petition
with tears of blood

08:02.000 --> 08:03.560
to first interrogate Marquis Muyang

08:03.920 --> 08:07.399
for his crimes of colluding with Cangbei
and trafficking weaponry.

08:08.319 --> 08:09.120
Second,

08:10.519 --> 08:12.600
to reopen the case
of the late Prince Ding Mo Xiuwen,

08:13.439 --> 08:15.439
who suffered a grave injustice.

08:16.959 --> 08:17.759
Third,

08:18.439 --> 08:20.959
to clear the thirty thousand
loyal Heiyun Cavalry souls' names

08:22.079 --> 08:24.399
and reveal the truth
of their deaths for the nation.

08:27.279 --> 08:29.759
I beg Your Majesties

08:31.079 --> 08:31.920
to grant my petition.

08:37.200 --> 08:39.200
I implore Your Majesties

08:39.440 --> 08:40.688
to grant his petition.

08:46.840 --> 08:48.759
- We second the motion.
- We second the motion.

08:59.000 --> 08:59.799
Granted.

09:22.320 --> 09:28.944
(Danque Gate)

09:37.840 --> 09:38.639
What's wrong, Li?

09:41.200 --> 09:42.480
To see Gu Zheng,

09:43.039 --> 09:44.840
I swallowed Han Mingxi's hairpin.

09:46.039 --> 09:48.480
It's fine. I already induced vomiting.

09:52.480 --> 09:53.519
You call this fine?

09:54.039 --> 09:55.240
Let's get a physician.

09:59.824 --> 10:03.920
(Tuisi Pavilion)

10:31.440 --> 10:32.799
Why is it hotter than yesterday?

10:41.159 --> 10:41.960
Li,

10:43.919 --> 10:46.399
I'm sorry. It was my negligence.

10:47.679 --> 10:48.519
Yao,

10:51.039 --> 10:52.440
I want to tell you,

10:55.399 --> 10:58.720
I got the edict
from Dowager Consort Qin.

10:59.679 --> 11:02.799
Don't talk now.
You're worse than yesterday.

11:03.279 --> 11:05.200
We'll talk when you're better, alright?

11:06.559 --> 11:07.679
Rest well for now.

11:34.919 --> 11:36.200
I'll enter the palace today.

11:36.279 --> 11:38.519
My wife still has a fever.
Take good care of her.

11:38.679 --> 11:41.039
Have the physician
check her again later.

11:41.919 --> 11:42.720
Yes.

12:08.919 --> 12:09.720
Qingshuang.

12:11.639 --> 12:12.879
Qingshuang, what's wrong?

12:14.480 --> 12:15.480
What's wrong?

12:18.919 --> 12:22.039
My Lady, I'm scared.

12:23.720 --> 12:27.000
Don't be afraid, Qingshuang.
We're both out of prison.

12:27.720 --> 12:29.440
We've returned to Prince Ding's Mansion.

12:31.279 --> 12:34.799
I'm afraid we'll be driven out.

12:41.000 --> 12:42.919
But we still have to tell him.

12:45.039 --> 12:47.240
We are the ones
who wanted to uncover this truth.

12:48.000 --> 12:49.720
So we shouldn't have any concealment.

12:51.240 --> 12:54.120
But if we don't tell him,
he won't find out.

12:57.080 --> 13:00.879
The truth is the truth.
It can't be hidden.

13:24.320 --> 13:26.000
No matter what the outcome,

13:27.039 --> 13:28.840
we must bear it.

13:30.039 --> 13:33.720
Didn't we decide this
when we came down the mountain?

13:34.720 --> 13:38.559
But I like Prince Ding's Mansion.

13:40.480 --> 13:41.559
I also like it.

13:43.480 --> 13:45.039
I also like His Highness.

13:47.879 --> 13:49.799
Can we tell him a little later?

13:50.639 --> 13:52.399
Well, he's very busy.

13:52.600 --> 13:54.159
He left just as dawn broke.

13:55.120 --> 13:56.799
Let's wait until this case is over.

13:57.679 --> 13:59.720
Let's tell him
after it's all over, alright?

14:04.000 --> 14:07.759
Alright. We'll wait
till this is all over.

14:19.408 --> 14:22.448
(Spring Serenity)

14:33.879 --> 14:36.559
Master, please put the flowerpot down.

14:36.559 --> 14:38.600
It's been three days.
Aren't your arms sore?

14:38.879 --> 14:40.200
(Qingfu)
Don't mind me.

14:42.840 --> 14:44.759
Master, look at yourself.

14:44.960 --> 14:46.879
Now you neglect everything
and don't go home.

14:47.000 --> 14:48.240
Aren't you sincere enough?

14:48.320 --> 14:50.559
I think that person from Cangbei
is just toying with you.

14:52.440 --> 14:53.480
Don't talk nonsense.

14:54.159 --> 14:55.360
You know what she's like?

14:58.720 --> 14:59.600
What happened?

14:59.679 --> 15:01.639
It seems like it is
that princess from Cangbei.

15:01.840 --> 15:03.039
How did she die?

15:03.799 --> 15:05.320
No wonder there was a curfew earlier.

15:06.639 --> 15:07.679
What a pity.

15:09.679 --> 15:11.240
Who is that in the prisoner cart?

15:11.840 --> 15:13.488
Looks like another person from Cangbei.

15:14.600 --> 15:16.399
The princess died here in Dachu.

15:16.639 --> 15:17.919
Are we going to war again?

15:17.919 --> 15:20.639
I hope not. My son is at Suixue Pass.

15:21.600 --> 15:23.080
They killed their own princess?

15:23.320 --> 15:24.440
Who knows?

15:25.799 --> 15:27.519
Look, what's going on?

15:27.840 --> 15:29.480
Isn't it the Cangbei delegation?

15:30.759 --> 15:31.879
Seems like it.

15:35.399 --> 15:38.200
- Master, could something have happened
- What happened?

15:38.440 --> 15:40.879
to your friend from Cangbei,
which is why she couldn't come?

15:42.879 --> 15:45.080
I was just talking nonsense. Ignore me.

15:47.679 --> 15:48.480
Wait for her here.

15:48.480 --> 15:49.279
Me?

16:07.240 --> 16:08.679
Qingyu, are you alright?

16:09.879 --> 16:11.679
- I'm fine.
- Thank goodness.

16:12.000 --> 16:13.200
Sit down and rest for a bit.

16:15.120 --> 16:16.600
Wait here. I'll get your medicine.

16:17.039 --> 16:18.080
Take it easy then.

16:21.799 --> 16:24.240
Are Tao's funeral arrangements finished?

16:26.120 --> 16:28.600
Jin took care of it,
and Ms. Wen also went.

16:31.600 --> 16:33.399
Your body hasn't fully recovered yet.

16:33.559 --> 16:36.919
The physician said you need to have
a liquid diet for 20 days to recuperate.

16:38.879 --> 16:39.679
Take your medicine.

16:44.399 --> 16:45.320
Not too bitter anymore?

16:46.960 --> 16:47.799
It's very bitter.

16:56.159 --> 16:57.000
Osmanthus candy?

16:58.039 --> 16:58.840
Is it sweet?

17:11.000 --> 17:13.240
You went to court today?

17:15.240 --> 17:16.599
What'll happen to Marquis Muyang?

17:19.200 --> 17:22.079
A joint trial by three judicial offices.
Gongshu Yang has also returned.

17:22.200 --> 17:24.559
The Huaixi weaponry case
was investigated thoroughly.

17:25.000 --> 17:27.200
Combined with Qin Cang's, Zheng Zuoshi's

17:27.319 --> 17:28.839
and Chen Longxiang's testimonies

17:29.200 --> 17:30.559
and the late emperor's edict,

17:31.440 --> 17:32.839
there is no room for reversal.

17:33.160 --> 17:34.559
He's been sent to death row.

17:35.000 --> 17:36.240
And what about Su Zuidie?

17:36.839 --> 17:38.680
Has the Cangbei delegation set off?

17:38.839 --> 17:39.920
They left this morning.

17:40.920 --> 17:41.920
Stop thinking about it.

17:42.839 --> 17:44.039
Your body is weak.

17:44.319 --> 17:46.000
Focus on your recuperation, alright?

17:51.200 --> 17:54.599
As I told you before,
Mo Jingli might still be alive.

17:55.440 --> 17:56.440
I suspect

17:56.559 --> 18:00.079
that Su Zuidie's assassination
of Princess Lingyun is connected to him.

18:02.319 --> 18:05.039
Mo Jingli and Su Zuidie
are both from the Eastern Palace.

18:05.839 --> 18:08.079
With Princess Lingyun dead in Dachu,

18:08.920 --> 18:12.200
if war breaks out,
they can reap the benefits.

18:12.640 --> 18:15.839
But the Empress Dowager
won't investigate this case.

18:16.319 --> 18:19.799
She calls it Cangbei's internal matter
and forbids us to investigate.

18:21.359 --> 18:23.480
He won't let it go so easily.

18:24.119 --> 18:27.319
At worst, he's just biding his time
and plotting schemes.

18:28.440 --> 18:31.079
Dachu has stood for a century,
ruling over vast lands.

18:31.480 --> 18:34.799
Those secretly hoping for its downfall
are not just Mo Jingli alone.

18:35.359 --> 18:38.000
It's simply a matter
of meeting the threat with force.

18:39.400 --> 18:42.839
Listen to you. What great spirit!

18:44.279 --> 18:45.079
Are you teasing me?

18:45.920 --> 18:46.720
I dare not.

18:49.480 --> 18:50.279
What's this?

18:53.640 --> 18:54.920
It's Princess Lingyun.

18:57.720 --> 18:58.559
You drew this?

19:00.640 --> 19:04.119
This princess was straightforward,
brave, and kind-hearted.

19:04.839 --> 19:08.519
If not for this incident, perhaps
we could have become friends.

19:12.759 --> 19:13.559
Your Highness.

19:17.759 --> 19:18.880
Master Feng is here.

19:32.920 --> 19:35.279
Mo Lao'er, you have to help me.

19:35.559 --> 19:36.359
What's wrong?

19:36.759 --> 19:39.640
It's about my friend from Cangbei.
We had agreed to meet.

19:39.640 --> 19:41.759
But it's been days,
and she still hasn't shown up.

19:42.240 --> 19:44.240
I searched all the inns in the capital,

19:44.720 --> 19:46.079
but there's no news of her at all.

19:46.759 --> 19:47.720
Even you can't find her?

19:48.920 --> 19:51.920
Perhaps she had urgent business
and left our capital early.

19:52.559 --> 19:53.519
That can't be.

19:55.599 --> 19:57.279
She already knew how I felt.

19:57.599 --> 19:59.119
We were just about to make it clear.

19:59.359 --> 20:00.759
Since we agreed to meet,

20:00.759 --> 20:02.319
she wouldn't miss it without a reason.

20:03.240 --> 20:06.440
I'm worried that maybe
she ran into some kind of accident

20:06.440 --> 20:07.920
or encountered some danger,

20:08.400 --> 20:09.920
so she couldn't show up.

20:10.960 --> 20:13.000
I remember you said she's from Cangbei.

20:14.240 --> 20:15.759
Did she come with the delegation?

20:16.160 --> 20:18.920
Their princess died.
Maybe she was forced to leave with them.

20:19.319 --> 20:20.759
She's just a merchant.

20:20.920 --> 20:24.200
She explicitly told me that this trip
to our capital was to purchase goods.

20:26.039 --> 20:27.920
The city was under
strict inspection earlier.

20:27.920 --> 20:31.680
All people from Cangbei were summoned
to the prefecture to register.

20:32.599 --> 20:35.200
I remember besides the delegation,
there were only five of them,

20:35.559 --> 20:36.759
three men and two women.

20:37.359 --> 20:39.720
All aged between forty and fifty

20:40.720 --> 20:42.480
and related to the capital's merchants.

20:47.359 --> 20:50.319
The day the Cangbei delegation arrived,
she came to Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

20:51.160 --> 20:52.720
When the Princess Lingyun died,

20:54.519 --> 20:55.880
she vanished without a trace.

20:58.640 --> 21:02.519
A coincidence.
It must be a coincidence, right?

21:02.839 --> 21:03.759
What's her name?

21:05.160 --> 21:06.079
Her name is Yun Ling.

21:09.039 --> 21:09.920
Yun Ling?

21:14.640 --> 21:15.519
Lingyun.

21:28.559 --> 21:29.480
Wait for me a moment.

21:35.079 --> 21:35.880
Lingyun?

21:55.759 --> 21:59.519
It's the Golden-Scaled Bloom
you mentioned liking in your letter.

22:00.559 --> 22:02.839
(When you go back to Cangbei,
I'll prepare some)

22:02.960 --> 22:03.880
(for you to take back.)

22:04.440 --> 22:05.880
(You're so thoughtful.)

22:09.759 --> 22:13.640
(My beloved is always evasive.)

22:14.608 --> 22:17.200
(Perhaps when you know
what she's hiding,)

22:17.599 --> 22:18.920
(you'll change your mind.)

22:19.640 --> 22:20.440
I won't.

22:22.400 --> 22:24.319
Alright. You won't.

22:27.319 --> 22:28.880
(What's that in your hand then?)

22:29.200 --> 22:30.440
(Something I carved for fun.)

22:30.440 --> 22:32.720
(The bone of an exorcism beast.
It tests fortune.)

22:33.279 --> 22:34.079
(How to test?)

22:34.960 --> 22:35.920
It's very simple.

22:36.119 --> 22:38.279
Toss it and see which side faces up.

22:38.759 --> 22:39.559
Let me test yours.

22:40.319 --> 22:41.160
Childish.

22:41.359 --> 22:42.319
Try it.

22:45.000 --> 22:45.799
Blow on it.

22:52.368 --> 22:53.279
(Auspicious)

22:53.279 --> 22:54.079
Auspicious.

22:55.000 --> 22:57.079
Boatman! Boatman!

22:58.039 --> 23:00.279
Did a group of Cangbei people
cross the river here?

23:00.519 --> 23:01.319
They just left.

23:01.960 --> 23:04.640
Look, they're on that big boat
in the distance.

23:19.839 --> 23:22.319
(Now, let's test your marriage fortune.)

23:23.039 --> 23:24.640
(See if you can find a good match)

23:24.640 --> 23:26.880
(on this trip to Dachu.)

23:30.096 --> 23:31.400
(Auspicious)

23:31.400 --> 23:32.920
Auspicious again?

23:33.559 --> 23:36.240
It seems your destined partner is here.

23:38.559 --> 23:41.440
(You and this token share a fate.
Take it as a gift.)

23:42.160 --> 23:44.079
(Alright. Thanks.)

23:48.319 --> 23:49.319
(I have a sister.)

23:50.039 --> 23:52.440
Her temperament is similar to mine,
and so are her looks.

23:54.039 --> 23:56.799
I'll let you two meet
in seven days, at the Shen hour.

23:58.400 --> 24:00.319
Under the old elm tree
by the Confucius Temple,

24:00.759 --> 24:04.039
I'll wait for you there with
the blooming Golden-Scaled Bloom.

24:05.920 --> 24:06.799
It's a deal.

24:07.799 --> 24:08.680
(Absolutely.)

24:13.759 --> 24:14.559
Lingyun!

24:17.319 --> 24:18.720
Golden-Scaled Bloom has bloomed.

24:20.359 --> 24:21.759
Can you see it?

25:26.000 --> 25:27.319
Why are you drinking alone?

25:30.559 --> 25:31.599
I'll join you.

25:36.720 --> 25:38.039
Even the bitterest wine

25:40.160 --> 25:41.880
leaves a hint of sweetness.

25:45.160 --> 25:48.319
But if you accidentally spill the wine,
and it seeps into the ground,

25:50.200 --> 25:52.240
you can never bring back its rich aroma.

26:15.960 --> 26:17.519
Who killed Lingyun?

26:18.559 --> 26:21.279
Her personal maid, Su Zuidie.

26:22.079 --> 26:23.480
Su Zuidie?

26:26.359 --> 26:28.039
Isn't she an old acquaintance of yours?

26:31.160 --> 26:32.039
Why?

26:35.079 --> 26:37.359
To sow discord
between Dachu and Cangbei.

26:52.920 --> 26:54.279
The people from Cangbei said

26:55.279 --> 26:58.400
that this item
did not belong to the Princess Lingyun.

26:58.559 --> 26:59.880
I recognized it when I saw it.

27:00.400 --> 27:01.319
It's yours, isn't it?

27:05.424 --> 27:09.104
(Auspicious)

27:10.960 --> 27:11.920
It's mine.

27:14.920 --> 27:16.119
I gave it to her.

27:22.119 --> 27:24.519
Tell me, if I had properly
read her fortune then,

27:26.160 --> 27:28.279
would she have been spared this tragedy?

27:40.496 --> 27:42.672
(Auspicious)

27:48.048 --> 27:51.088
(Qingtang Posthouse)

28:41.839 --> 28:44.640
It's almost completely dark.
Aren't we leaving yet?

28:45.200 --> 28:47.119
I'm almost drained dry by
the mosquitoes.

28:49.559 --> 28:50.920
Fan her for me.

28:57.480 --> 29:01.039
Your Highness, perhaps
I should escort you back first?

29:05.279 --> 29:08.000
Forget it. We've been
keeping him company all day.

29:08.319 --> 29:10.200
I want to see if this fisherman

29:10.200 --> 29:11.559
can catch anything today.

29:14.359 --> 29:16.559
Your Highness, you may not know.

29:16.880 --> 29:19.519
But ever since His Highness's
legs were injured,

29:20.160 --> 29:22.160
fishing has been
his only remaining hobby.

29:22.799 --> 29:25.920
And, the truth is,
I had people carefully select

29:26.000 --> 29:28.480
those fish in the mansion's pond.

29:28.480 --> 29:30.480
They are stupid fish
that bite at any bait.

29:31.119 --> 29:33.440
But these fish in the wild are smart.

29:33.519 --> 29:36.200
I feel that with His Highness's skills,

29:37.160 --> 29:38.880
he wouldn't catch one even by dawn.

29:43.920 --> 29:44.799
- It bit?
- It bit?

29:58.599 --> 30:01.039
What kind of fish is this?
It's quite pretty.

30:02.599 --> 30:03.720
Given its bright tail,

30:04.440 --> 30:07.519
it should be an immature
silver-tailed fish.

30:08.160 --> 30:09.079
A silver-tailed fish?

30:10.720 --> 30:12.559
Isn't that the priciest fish
on the market?

30:12.640 --> 30:14.920
The wealthy families in the capital
would fight over them.

30:15.440 --> 30:17.319
You actually caught one
with just one cast?

30:17.319 --> 30:18.559
Your Highness is truly amazing!

30:21.559 --> 30:22.920
Let's take it back home,

30:23.160 --> 30:25.000
raise it well, and wait for it to grow.

30:25.119 --> 30:27.319
No need to wait. I'll come back tomorrow

30:27.759 --> 30:28.920
and get a bigger one for you.

30:34.039 --> 30:34.839
Great.

30:42.079 --> 30:42.880
What's wrong?

30:44.359 --> 30:45.160
It's so itchy.

30:49.559 --> 30:50.359
Where?

30:57.440 --> 30:58.759
It's a cocklebur seed.

30:58.920 --> 31:00.400
They're everywhere on the mountain.

31:08.559 --> 31:10.119
Why do you have white hair?

31:14.960 --> 31:16.200
It runs in my family.

31:17.400 --> 31:20.640
When my brother was young,
stress would turn his hair white.

31:21.240 --> 31:22.319
My father was even more so.

31:23.160 --> 31:26.000
By the age of forty, his hair
was already completely gray.

31:27.200 --> 31:29.400
The medical books
call this premature graying.

31:29.519 --> 31:31.839
You should eat more black rice
and black sesame seeds.

31:32.640 --> 31:36.039
Physician Ye, this is
a hereditary condition.

31:36.559 --> 31:37.440
It can't be cured.

31:39.119 --> 31:40.799
Then can I dye your hair for you?

31:42.440 --> 31:43.599
Why should we dye my hair?

31:45.400 --> 31:48.039
Do you find my white hair ugly
and dislike it?

31:49.160 --> 31:52.559
No, it's not ugly.

31:56.279 --> 31:57.839
Then why aren't you looking at me?

32:08.119 --> 32:10.960
Your Highnesses, the carriage is ready.

32:16.559 --> 32:19.359
It's getting late. Let's go home
after we finish the roast meat.

32:30.736 --> 32:32.400
(Shende Shop)

32:55.568 --> 32:58.448
(Tuisi Pavilion)

33:01.599 --> 33:03.000
Senior, what's wrong with you?

33:05.599 --> 33:07.720
I've caught a chill and can't get cold.

33:10.319 --> 33:11.248
Where is Prince Ding?

33:12.119 --> 33:13.039
He went to the office.

33:15.000 --> 33:16.559
Marquis Muyang is already in prison.

33:16.640 --> 33:17.759
Why is he still so busy?

33:19.079 --> 33:21.759
The Marquis Muyang case
implicates many officials.

33:22.160 --> 33:26.160
The Empress Dowager put him,
Murong Shen, and Gongshu Yang on it.

33:28.440 --> 33:31.640
What comes next?
Have you figured out what to do?

33:35.200 --> 33:39.000
Deeper digging on the edict means
more people will be implicated.

33:39.680 --> 33:41.240
If they find out about your mother,

33:41.400 --> 33:43.400
how will you manage
in this mansion afterwards?

33:43.839 --> 33:45.160
And how will Mo Xiuyao treat you?

33:48.359 --> 33:50.200
The situation is indeed complicated.

33:51.160 --> 33:53.119
Being able to fulfil
my promise to Mo Xiuwen

33:53.680 --> 33:55.200
is already the greatest comfort.

33:56.880 --> 33:57.920
As for Yao,

33:58.359 --> 34:01.400
I will find an appropriate time
to explain everything to him.

34:02.759 --> 34:05.759
Don't worry, Senior. Yao promised me

34:06.160 --> 34:09.400
that no matter what happens,
he will never abandon me

34:10.000 --> 34:11.519
or leave me alone.

34:12.360 --> 34:13.239
I believe him.

34:19.800 --> 34:22.519
Why don't you take it off?
You look so hot.

34:23.119 --> 34:23.920
It's fine.

34:25.920 --> 34:26.800
Take it off.

34:28.320 --> 34:29.079
Who did this?

34:33.880 --> 34:37.199
It looks like a scratch.

34:39.840 --> 34:40.760
I guessed right?

34:41.920 --> 34:43.840
It's a nail mark from Lady Yusheng?

34:47.800 --> 34:51.159
I'll talk. I'll talk, alright?

34:54.360 --> 34:57.800
Yusheng is simply too unreasonable.

34:58.440 --> 35:00.960
She has a close sworn friend
who is a guqin player.

35:01.239 --> 35:02.960
The two of them are about the same age.

35:03.120 --> 35:05.599
They're often together.
playing the guqin and dancing.

35:06.000 --> 35:09.360
One day, I saw a new man's robe
in her room.

35:09.519 --> 35:11.920
I thought it was made for me,
so I put it on.

35:11.920 --> 35:13.639
And she got upset.

35:14.920 --> 35:16.960
The robe was made
for that guqin player, wasn't it?

35:17.679 --> 35:18.800
Who else could it be for?

35:19.320 --> 35:20.800
Did you lose your temper with her?

35:21.800 --> 35:25.239
I didn't. I tried to reason
with her nicely.

35:25.519 --> 35:27.679
I told her that the robe
fit me quite well

35:27.679 --> 35:29.320
and offered to give her money,

35:29.320 --> 35:31.719
so she could buy some fabric
to make him a new one.

35:31.760 --> 35:32.599
She didn't agree.

35:32.880 --> 35:35.559
Then I offered to buy her freedom,

35:35.559 --> 35:37.400
so she and that man could be together

35:37.440 --> 35:38.719
and roam the realm together.

35:38.719 --> 35:40.360
That would be considered a good match.

35:40.599 --> 35:41.960
But she suddenly went mad,

35:42.079 --> 35:44.000
ran over, and scratched and bit me.

35:44.360 --> 35:46.400
Look, look at this scratch.

35:46.599 --> 35:48.440
And my wrist. She bit it until it bled.

35:49.039 --> 35:51.960
She went hard on me.
She's a crazy woman.

35:53.159 --> 35:55.000
So stupid.

35:55.519 --> 35:57.360
She's not stupid but crazy.

35:57.679 --> 35:58.800
You are stupid.

36:02.000 --> 36:04.360
You can recite swordsmanship
and military tactics by heart,

36:04.639 --> 36:06.920
but you are clueless
about a woman's heart.

36:10.039 --> 36:12.119
Am I stupid?

36:21.360 --> 36:23.000
Where is your Senior Li?

36:26.159 --> 36:27.000
He left.

36:27.559 --> 36:29.000
He's not staying for dinner?

36:29.039 --> 36:31.320
I ordered the kitchen
to prepare many dishes.

36:31.880 --> 36:33.239
He's not in the mood to eat.

36:33.760 --> 36:34.559
Why?

36:34.880 --> 36:35.960
He's love-struck.

36:37.840 --> 36:39.800
Here, have some snacks first.

36:40.599 --> 36:42.213
It's five wen each, my lady.

36:44.880 --> 36:46.128
(Xiangqi Pavilion)
There are new styles. Look at it.

36:47.880 --> 36:48.679
Master.

37:03.239 --> 37:04.039
Master Li,

37:04.679 --> 37:07.559
Lady Yusheng went to Xihua
for a performance. Didn't she tell you?

37:08.280 --> 37:09.400
That guqin player also went?

37:09.599 --> 37:12.119
Of course, they went together.

37:22.960 --> 37:23.840
Master Mingxi?

37:24.519 --> 37:26.760
What? It's been so long
that you don't recognize me?

37:27.960 --> 37:28.800
Where is my brother?

37:30.199 --> 37:32.559
Master Mingxi, Master Mingyue
is currently unavailable.

37:32.559 --> 37:34.320
Let me take you
to the side hall to wait.

37:34.320 --> 37:36.000
Why can't I see my own brother?

37:38.079 --> 37:40.760
I failed in my duty.
Please punish me, Your Highness.

37:41.079 --> 37:42.000
Who is inside?

37:42.920 --> 37:44.159
That sorceress is back?

37:44.920 --> 37:46.280
Master Mingxi,

37:46.320 --> 37:47.599
the family head is inside.

37:47.760 --> 37:50.719
My father died long ago.
Who is my family head?

37:59.119 --> 38:00.599
Did you think I didn't know?

38:02.599 --> 38:05.119
You and Prince Ding
share a childhood bond.

38:06.320 --> 38:08.840
Seeing Mo Xiuyao's heart
set on someone else,

38:09.880 --> 38:11.920
you thought of tearing her to pieces.

38:13.559 --> 38:15.360
But did I not say

38:16.239 --> 38:18.800
no one is allowed to harm her?

38:19.320 --> 38:22.199
Your Highness, have mercy.
Zuidie just had a moment of foolishness.

38:22.880 --> 38:24.360
I beg Your Highness to forgive her.

38:24.480 --> 38:26.960
She knows Cangbei's tribes.
She's still useful.

38:28.679 --> 38:29.480
Useful?

38:30.440 --> 38:31.119
Yes.

38:31.760 --> 38:34.000
Zuidie has been undercover
in Cangbei for many years.

38:34.280 --> 38:36.239
She can link us to Cangbei's tribes.

38:36.239 --> 38:37.920
Moreover, she is loyal and devoted

38:37.920 --> 38:39.639
and has repeatedly proven her worth.

38:39.639 --> 38:41.199
I beg Your Highness to forgive her.

38:41.840 --> 38:45.320
What you say makes sense.

38:47.679 --> 38:48.880
But if it's not her fault,

38:50.384 --> 38:51.376
whose fault is it then?

38:55.480 --> 38:56.840
Han Mingyue.

38:58.320 --> 38:59.360
Master Mingxi!

38:59.679 --> 39:00.599
Mingyue!

39:04.280 --> 39:05.079
You!

39:05.079 --> 39:06.920
Mingxi, don't be reckless.

39:07.840 --> 39:09.119
Why did you hurt my brother?

39:13.800 --> 39:15.920
Your brother has truly
protected you well.

39:16.719 --> 39:20.320
All these years, he never even
told you who you truly serve

39:20.840 --> 39:23.360
or who your real enemy is.

39:25.519 --> 39:28.119
Your Highness, it's all my fault.

39:28.480 --> 39:30.000
Mingxi is still young.

39:30.119 --> 39:31.960
He knows nothing about the past.

39:32.320 --> 39:35.039
Zuidie's mistake this time
is also due to my lax discipline.

39:37.599 --> 39:39.519
Please, Your Highness,
spare us this one time.

39:39.800 --> 39:41.840
It will never happen again.

39:42.239 --> 39:43.920
Why are you bowing and scraping to him?

39:45.519 --> 39:46.800
So what if you're Prince Li?

39:47.159 --> 39:48.840
The Hans were wiped out eight years ago.

39:49.159 --> 39:50.639
The Eastern Palace has fallen too.

39:51.039 --> 39:52.840
Having survived until now,
we two brothers

39:53.079 --> 39:55.360
have nothing to do with the Hans
or the Eastern Palace.

39:55.840 --> 39:59.360
I'm telling you,
we won't work for you anymore.

40:05.840 --> 40:08.559
Without me or Prince Li's Mansion,

40:09.199 --> 40:10.440
you two brothers

40:10.840 --> 40:13.199
would have been nothing
but dust years ago.

40:16.360 --> 40:18.559
Do you really think you can shake
the Han family's mark?

40:19.360 --> 40:23.039
Do you really think you're clear
of the Eastern Palace case?

40:24.280 --> 40:27.840
Identity is a brand etched
into your blood and bones.

40:28.639 --> 40:31.360
You can't escape it,
nor can you tear it away.

40:33.119 --> 40:34.280
You think you are free,

40:35.239 --> 40:37.559
because your brother
has been carrying it all for you.

40:37.559 --> 40:38.519
If it weren't for him,

40:39.239 --> 40:42.719
the one suffering here
today would be you.

40:49.760 --> 40:51.599
I never force anyone to come aboard.

40:52.440 --> 40:55.599
But once you're on my ship,
you must follow my rules.

40:57.199 --> 40:58.159
Take your brother along.

40:58.840 --> 40:59.960
If he runs away,

41:01.480 --> 41:02.800
atone for it with your life.

41:05.119 --> 41:06.199
I understand.

41:11.559 --> 41:12.960
How are you?

41:17.760 --> 41:18.960
What are you doing here?

41:19.719 --> 41:21.599
Weren't you escorted back to Cangbei?

41:24.159 --> 41:28.039
It was you. You rescued her again?

41:29.800 --> 41:31.000
I'll kill you!

41:31.599 --> 41:32.280
Stop!

41:34.719 --> 41:36.000
Have you two forgotten

41:36.840 --> 41:39.920
how we survived the exile
eight years ago?

41:40.519 --> 41:43.719
Now, if we lose even one of us three,

41:44.159 --> 41:45.400
none of us can survive.

41:46.599 --> 41:48.360
Zuidie, go.

42:08.000 --> 42:11.800
Mingxi, we no longer
have any way out now.

42:12.159 --> 42:14.800
As long as the Eastern Palace rises,
things will be alright.

42:14.800 --> 42:15.599
Will they?

42:16.159 --> 42:19.360
Do you really think he'll make you
a key official when he's the Emperor?

42:20.360 --> 42:22.760
You know very well how many dirty deeds

42:23.239 --> 42:24.760
you've done for him.

42:26.280 --> 42:27.960
If he ever wants to walk in the light,

42:28.320 --> 42:30.199
the first person he'll silence is you.

42:30.719 --> 42:32.159
His Highness is not like that.

42:32.480 --> 42:33.360
Zuidie and I believe...

42:33.360 --> 42:34.360
Don't mention her again.

42:35.320 --> 42:37.280
You really are enchanted
by that sorceress.

42:39.344 --> 42:42.192
(Preview)

42:43.119 --> 42:45.039
Marquis Muyang
suddenly asked to see you.

42:45.400 --> 42:47.480
He won't let it go so easily.

42:47.760 --> 42:49.039
If it were Zhou Tianyang,

42:49.360 --> 42:52.119
would you also silence him
for your own safety?

42:52.679 --> 42:54.159
Life must go on,

42:54.599 --> 42:57.440
but how we live it isn't set in stone.

42:59.280 --> 43:02.679
Ye Li, could I still have a chance?

43:03.280 --> 43:05.159
Can you let Qingshuang
go back to her own home?

43:06.039 --> 43:07.880
But Qingshuang has always been with me.

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
♪Unbound by form♪
